These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, iced-tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, radish, pear, lemon
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, traveling, skydiving, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, ambient, country, trance
4 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, snake, ferret
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, golf, swimming
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, ship, motorbike, taxi
 1. the person eating blueberry is between the person drinking juice and the owner of the mouse##2
 2. the person eating pear is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 6. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 7. the fan of ambient is between the person driving the ship and the owner of the ferret##2
 8. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person eating lemon is the fan of hip-hop##1
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person eating radish##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
12. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
13. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
14. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
15. the fan of country is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea        | mirinda     | cola | juice      |
| Food          | pear | radish    | blueberry      | lemon  |
| Hobby         | traveling  | puzzles    | photography       | skydiving     |
| Music-Genre   | country        | trance       | ambient          | hip-hop |
| Pet           | snake    | mouse | pony      | ferret     |
| Sport         | surfing   | biathlon   | golf      | swimming    |
| Transport     | train        | ship        | taxi    | motorbike    |

