The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, surfing, lacrosse, handball
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, van, train, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the owner of the ferret##1
 5. the person watching superhero movies is the person eating raspberry##1
 6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is the person driving the van##1
 9. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person eating plum is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
12. the person eating plum is between the person driving the train and the person eating apple##2
13. the person watching western movies is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
14. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
15. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1

